1
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:50,680
Alright.

2
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,600
Class, stop writing.

3
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,090
I have an announcement to make.

4
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,610
Class monitor Xing Yaqi

5
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,400
has a vocal grade exam coming up,

6
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,280
so she won't be able to join the cheer squad.

7
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,080
I propose

8
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,920
that the cheer squad captain

9
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,400
be Gu Xinrui.

10
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,440
Does anyone have any objections?

11
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,240
Mr. Tian.

12
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,440
Cheerleading requires teamwork.

13
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,640
I think we should find someone we are more familiar with

14
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,720
to be the captain.

15
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,760
We might have better chemistry.

16
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,680
You might not know this,

17
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,200
but Gu Xinrui

18
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,600
has ten years of ballroom dancing experience

19
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,240
and has even won a national gold award.

20
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,160
Not only that,

21
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,360
for three years in middle school,

22
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,200
she was the captain of the school's cheer squad.

23
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,760
Moreover, she represented the school

24
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,360
in the provincial competition

25
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,960
and won the championship.

26
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,040
Today,

27
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,880
Gu Xinrui, the music teacher, and I

28
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,400
discussed this in class.

29
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:39,400
For the format of our cheerleading squad,

30
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,680
she provided a lot of constructive advice.

31
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,520
So,

32
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,320
the music teacher and I thought it was great.

33
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,000
After discussing with the other teachers, we decided

34
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,800
that the captain of the cheerleading squad

35
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,280
will be Gu Xinrui.

36
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,240
I disagree.

37
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,000
Jingu.

38
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,240
You have a back injury. You can't dance yet.

39
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,800
I won't directly participate in the cheerleading performance.

40
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,320
If you don't directly participate in the performance,

41
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,650
why are you the captain?

42
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,680
I know I just joined our class,

43
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,480
and I'm not very familiar with everyone yet.

44
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,160
But since I've joined this class,

45
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:16,079
I am a member of it.

46
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,079
I also hope to

47
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,600
make my own contribution to the class.

48
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:22,400
However, I'm injured and can't perform.

49
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,000
But when I was abroad,

50
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,920
I saw some professional

51
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,320
cheerleading routines.

52
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,240
And I've also participated in some professional cheerleading performances.

53
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,800
So I'd like to be your captain.

54
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:34,640
I have no problem taking charge of the overall situation.

55
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,840
However, if anyone

56
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,380
thinks I'm not qualified,

57
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,890
I accept the challenge.

58
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,860
We can compete fairly for the captain position,

59
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:43,560
right?

60
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:48,200
Does anyone have a good candidate?

61
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,850
Mu Qingjun recommends Xiong Yuanbao.

62
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,320
Yes, I recommend Xiong Yuanbao.

63
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,880
Are you crazy?

64
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,040
Xiong Yuanbao.

65
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,080
Mr. Tian, I don't want to participate.

66
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,000
I've never been in a cheerleading squad before.

67
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,240
I can't do it.

68
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,040
Mr. Tian.

69
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:12,520
During the last drama performance.

70
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,520
During the last drama performance,

71
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,720
I'm sure everyone saw

72
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,360
Yuanbao's understanding and hard work.

73
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,560
I believe it will be the same this time.

74
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,880
She will definitely play the role of captain well

75
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,640
and win honor for our class.

76
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,320
What are you talking about?

77
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,720
Mr. Tian, I agree with Mu Qingyun.

78
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,440
We are all Chinese kids.

79
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:29,200
We can't handle those foreign things.

80
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,400
We won't be used to them.

81
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,330
Traditional methods suit us best.

82
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,760
Mr. Tian.

83
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:38,200
I think although the captain can control the big picture,

84
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,640
if the captain doesn't step up personally,

85
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,850
then to the other team members,

86
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,240
it wouldn't be very convincing.

87
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,720
Well.

88
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:51,000
I agree to let Xiong Yuanbao be the captain too.

89
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,240
I agree too.

90
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,120
In that case,

91
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,920
whoever supports Yuanbao as the cheer captain,

92
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,250
please raise your hand.

93
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,000
Agreed.

94
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:10,580
All right. I accept Xiong Yuanbao's challenge.

95
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,540
Those who want to join my team,

96
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,320
please raise your hands.

97
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,520
Yuanbao,

98
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,400
let's each form a cheerleading squad.

99
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:28,000
We'll compete before the basketball game

100
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,800
to see whose is better.

101
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,080
The winning team

102
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,220
will perform at the basketball game.

103
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,000
What do you think?

104
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,920
Okay, you're on.

105
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,240
If you want to show off

106
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,560
in this way,

107
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,000
I have no objections.

108
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,680
The winning team

109
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:52,220
will perform at the basketball game.

110
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,880
Okay, that's all. Class dismissed.

111
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,520
Stand up.

112
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,240
Goodbye, sir.

113
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,360
Goodbye, class.

114
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,200
It's fine.

115
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,080
I will help you.

116
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,800
What are you doing?

117
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,600
Weren't you ignoring me before?

118
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,400
When did I say I'd ignore you?

119
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,240
You're overthinking it.

120
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,200
Overthinking?

121
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,520
You are lying through your teeth.

122
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:41,600
Right.

123
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:45,120
You nominated me to be the cheer captain today.

124
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,480
Did you just want to see me make a fool of myself?

125
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:50,040
I've been uncoordinated since I was a kid.

126
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,320
You want me to dance in the cheerleading squad.

127
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,650
What do you mean by that?

128
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,240
Xiaoxiong.

129
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,170
I have to criticize you.

130
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:01,180
Why is your thinking going downhill lately?

131
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:04,120
Where did your innate,

132
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,560
almost what you'd call

133
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,400
shameless confidence go?

134
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,740
Screw you. You're the shameless one.

135
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,360
Alright.

136
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,840
I know missing the last drama performance

137
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,700
has always been a regret of yours.

138
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:18,100
Consider this making up for that regret.

139
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,960
Don't worry, with me here,

140
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,600
it's no big deal.

141
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,160
I'll sort it all out for you.

142
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,960
We've already

143
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,840
prepared a bunch of cheerleading

144
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,880
practice materials for you.

145
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,720
Really.

146
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:29,760
Of course.

147
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,159
Otherwise, how could I take on so much for you?

148
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,520
Thank you, Mutou.

149
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,200
You are so sweet.

150
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:35,960
Thank you.

151
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,880
You should have told me earlier.

152
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,440
You scared me to death.

153
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,480
When I heard I was going to be the captain,

154
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,880
my head almost exploded.

155
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,690
You're so hopeless.

156
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,960
This time, just pretend

157
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,560
you're playing the role of a cheer captain.

158
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,530
Why are you sighing?

159
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,840
Gu Xinrui

160
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,500
does both ballroom dance and cheerleading,

161
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,370
both domestically and abroad.

162
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,980
How can I compare with her?

163
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,920
Yuanbao.

164
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,480
Actually, winning or losing is not important.

165
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,960
What's important is that you participate.

166
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,920
As long as you try your best,

167
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,080
that's the most precious thing.

168
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,960
Don't worry, don't pressure yourself.

169
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,490
We will always support you.

170
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,480
Mutou.

171
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,840
What's wrong?

172
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,680
Thank you.

173
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,410
I will do my best.

174
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,240
Don't mention it.

175
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,240
If you really mean it,

176
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,680
buy your brother some ice cream,

177
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,080
KFC, and stuff like that.

178
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,000
I remember, I remember it all.

179
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,770
What else do you want to eat?

180
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,240
The day after tomorrow is the weekend.

181
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:47,360
You two will stay home and study.

182
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,650
You're not allowed to go anywhere.

183
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:50,960
Got it.

184
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,840
You're already high school juniors.

185
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,080
Why join the basketball cheerleading squad?

186
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,540
It's a total waste of time.

187
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:59,440
Why not use that energy to do some practice tests?

188
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,680
You cannot go to this event.

189
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,610
I don't approve.

190
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,250
I also disagree.

191
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,680
Grandma,

192
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:07,480
I'm just participating in the class activity.

193
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,240
And I'm the captain this time.

194
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:12,000
There's going to be a competition in the class.

195
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,280
It's a rare opportunity.

196
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,160
So what if you get first place?

197
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,080
Will it add points to your college entrance exam?

198
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,680
Look at what grade you're in.

199
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:21,340
Still thinking about these useless things.

200
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,320
Grandma, Yuanbao has been doing well

201
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,440
in school recently.

202
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,480
Mr. Tian even praised her for her progress.

203
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,200
Mr. Tian also said

204
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,560
that this activity won't affect her studies.

205
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,960
Instead, it can

206
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,000
strike a balance between work and rest.

207
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,930
That's right, Grandma.

208
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:52,000
Haven't you always supported me?

209
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,920
I do support you.

210
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,920
I support you exercising

211
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,280
and studying hard.

212
00:09:59,360 --> 00:09:59,960
But you said it yourself,

213
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:02,080
you've never danced before.

214
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,980
You hurt your eye acting in a play.

215
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,280
Your aunt and I

216
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,120
were scared to death at the time.

217
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,320
Grandma, don't worry.

218
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,480
It's just physical training this time.

219
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,940
There won't be any danger.

220
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,560
That's right, Grandma.

221
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,960
Our teacher said we need to enhance our physical fitness

222
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,240
to handle the junior and senior years'

223
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,240
high-pressure studying.

224
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,700
High pressure?

225
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,920
I don't see any high pressure on you two at all.

226
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,840
You look completely relaxed to me.

227
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,570
Mu Qingyun, you are not allowed to speak anymore.

228
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,680
I will call your teacher tomorrow.

229
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:39,010
You cannot participate in this activity.

230
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,040
Mom, how could you do this?

231
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:40,760
Do what?

232
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,000
If you score

233
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,480
just a few points again on this exam,

234
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,760
see how I deal with you.

235
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,680
Grandma.

236
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,040
I must

237
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,720
participate in the activity this time.

238
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,660
I have to participate.

239
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,560
This activity has nothing to do with studying.

240
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,760
What if something bad happens to you?

241
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,440
You're killing me.

242
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,240
Grandma.

243
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,760
No, no, no.

244
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:12,840
Look.

245
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:14,600
Don't be mad at her.

246
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,400
Yuanbao.

247
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,440
Aren't you a sensible child?

248
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,980
Why won't you listen to us?

249
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,640
I'm sorry, Grandma.

250
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,280
Grandma, I'm sorry.

251
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:24,480
It's fine.

252
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:26,780
As long as you don't go.

253
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,920
Eat your food.

254
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:32,080
I'm full. I'll go back first.

255
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:38,330
Aunt Wenying, please don't be mad.

256
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,080
I'll talk to her later.

257
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,800
She is a sensible child,

258
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,480
and will understand your intentions.

259
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,120
Grandma.

260
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,560
I'm sorry.

261
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,880
I apologize on behalf of Yuanbao.

262
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,320
She didn't mean that.

263
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,680
I am just worried...

264
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:56,000
I am just worried about her safety.

265
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,960
I also agree to let Xiong Yuanbao be the captain.

266
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,720
I agree too.

267
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,440
Those of us who support Yuanbao as cheerleading captain,

268
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,440
raise your hands.

269
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,040
What should we do?

270
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:12,400
Five, six, seven, eight.

271
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,480
What else?

272
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,560
And then what?

273
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:16,760
Yuanbao.

274
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,730
What's wrong, Yuanbao?

275
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:26,010
I have something to tell everyone.

276
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:28,680
I'm sorry for letting you all down.

277
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,640
The cheerleading competition,

278
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,740
I can't participate in it.

279
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,520
Keep up the good work for me.

280
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,000
What's going on?

281
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,520
What's the problem?

282
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,760
We can solve it together.

283
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,160
Yeah, we are here for you.

284
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,700
My grandma doesn't agree.

285
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,040
She got really angry.

286
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:51,000
I don't want to make her sad anymore.

287
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,000
So, I'm sorry.

288
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,400
It's fine.

289
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,240
Then are we still competing?

290
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,360
Forget it.

291
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,560
If you don't participate,

292
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:02,220
we won't participate either.

293
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,280
We're not participating.

294
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:06,880
Actually, you don't have to be too afraid of us.

295
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,250
Who's afraid of you?

296
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,400
If you're not afraid, why not participate?

297
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,720
Just surrender.

298
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,890
What is there to be embarrassed about?

299
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:15,290
What are you saying?

300
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,530
It's good that you quit now.

301
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,000
You won't lose too badly

302
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,080
and lose face.

303
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:35,920
Have you made up your minds

304
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:38,180
that you definitely won't participate?

305
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:40,520
We've discussed it.

306
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:42,880
We won't participate

307
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,360
in this cheerleading competition.

308
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:46,800
Actually,

309
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:50,160
I still highly encourage you to participate.

310
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:51,420
Because in the future,

311
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,840
your studies will get more and more intense.

312
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,120
While you still have some time,

313
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,720
it's not a bad thing to exercise more.

314
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,380
Besides, many years from now,

315
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:58,560
you probably won't remember

316
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,620
this midterm exam,

317
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,520
but you will definitely remember

318
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:02,320
the beautiful times

319
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:04,920
you spent together in the cheerleading squad.

320
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,040
Alright.

321
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,840
If you've made up your minds,

322
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:09,210
then let's just drop it.

323
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:10,280
Excuse me.

324
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,530
Teacher, please wait a moment.

325
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,960
Grandma.

326
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,920
Grandma, why are you here?

327
00:15:32,040 --> 00:15:32,880
Mr. Tian,

328
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:35,540
Yuanbao and the others will join.

329
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,680
Grandma,

330
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,880
I'm not participating anymore.

331
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:41,280
Aren't you always clumsy and getting hurt?

332
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,800
I sewed you some knee pads.

333
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:47,040
Wear them during practice.

334
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,960
If anything happened to you,

335
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,840
it would be the end of me.

336
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,400
I was just worried

337
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:03,680
about her safety.

338
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,480
When I was in school,

339
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,160
I was also a cheerleader.

340
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:33,320
Now, when dancing in the square,

341
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,600
I'm still the team leader.

342
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,840
I can teach you.

343
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:37,640
Mr. Tian,

344
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:40,280
Yuanbao and the others will surely do well.

345
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:45,680
But let's make things clear first.

346
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,480
In front of Mr. Tian,

347
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:49,400
can you promise to improve

348
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,840
in the next exam?

349
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:55,440
Thank you, Grandma. I'll do my best.

350
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:59,280
I promise I'll improve in the next exam.

351
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,320
Thank you, Grandma.

352
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,640
What's this?

353
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,120
I downloaded some good

354
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,480
cheerleading dance videos.

355
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,640
I hope they help you.

356
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:01,480
Thank you. You're so thoughtful.

357
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:03,680
But...

358
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:05,720
But what?

359
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:09,680
But I'm in a competition with Gu Xinrui right now.

360
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:12,460
If she knew you were helping me like this,

361
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:14,480
she would probably be unhappy.

362
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,520
I told you,

363
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:18,530
Xinrui and I just grew up together like siblings.

364
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:20,840
And right now her waist is injured.

365
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:22,960
I don't want her to win this time.

366
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,360
What if her waist wasn't injured?

367
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:31,040
There is no 'what if'.

368
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:31,680
I

369
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,330
just want you to win.

370
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:37,480
It's fine. Don't worry.

371
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:40,160
We're just participating for fun.

372
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,400
Besides, we are too amateur.

373
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,040
We definitely won't win.

374
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,840
You have to believe in yourself.

375
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:47,560
I support you. Come on.

376
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:50,520
Take it.

377
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,320
Thank you, deskmate.

378
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,610
Let's go back first.

379
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,120
Yuanbao.

380
00:19:03,560 --> 00:19:05,090
You have huge dark circles.

381
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,960
Didn't you sleep well last night?

382
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:08,840
I had a nightmare last night.

383
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,840
What kind of nightmare? Tell me about it.

384
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:12,100
I...

385
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:12,770
Yuanbao.

386
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,280
I have something to tell you.

387
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:16,240
But class is about to start.

388
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,980
It's fine. It won't take long.

389
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,130
Ruirui, go back to class first.

390
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,840
I'll be right back.

391
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:27,300
Don't worry. I'll be fine.

392
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:36,500
What do you want to talk about?

393
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:39,320
I heard your parents passed away years ago

394
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,320
in a firecracker factory accident.

395
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,440
You were raised by your grandmother.

396
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,440
Your family must be under a lot of financial pressure, right?

397
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,640
You investigated me?

398
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,900
That's not important.

399
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:50,680
What matters is that right now,

400
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:53,080
you have a chance to relieve your financial pressure,

401
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:56,210
as long as you are willing to drop out of the competition.

402
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:01,000
Do you think

403
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,680
you're so great just because you have some dirty money?

404
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:05,200
It can solve many problems you can't even imagine.

405
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:07,160
Do you think you're in an idol drama?

406
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:09,220
You've read too many romance novels.

407
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,000
Don't push your luck.

408
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,640
I'm pushing my luck?

409
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,440
You're the one pushing your luck.

410
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:17,640
I never thought you'd say something like this.

411
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:19,320
You used to be sarcastic to me,

412
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:20,720
and I could ignore it.

413
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,120
But for you to say something like this,

414
00:20:23,120 --> 00:20:24,580
you really opened my eyes.

415
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:26,000
Xiong Yuanbao.

416
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,880
Should I call you naive,

417
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:30,640
or too mature?

418
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,520
It seems we are not on the same path.

419
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:38,000
We're not suited to be friends.

420
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:40,000
Let's keep our distance from now on.

421
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:42,480
I will return the things you gave me.

422
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:45,160
Who knows what schemes are behind them.

423
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:04,280
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

424
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:05,680
Just you wait.

425
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,120
Did she bully you?

426
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,560
Who do you think I am?

427
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,080
How could she, with her weak little body,

428
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,240
possibly bully me?

429
00:21:22,840 --> 00:21:24,640
Let's go. Time to go home and eat.

430
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:35,520
Uncle Zhang.

431
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:36,400
Miss.

432
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,530
Can you find someone for me?

433
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,440
Who?

434
00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:43,690
Brother Shui, a dropout from Peiying Middle School.

435
00:21:46,760 --> 00:21:47,640
Class dismissed.

436
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,320
Stand up.

437
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:52,360
Goodbye, teacher.

438
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,440
Yuanbao, let's go to the restroom.

439
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,440
No, you go ahead.

440
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,420
How's the practice going?

441
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,040
Just so-so.

442
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,560
I know a dance teacher.

443
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:09,040
She promised to lend me

444
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,560
the dance studio this weekend.

445
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:11,360
Do you need it?

446
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:14,200
It doesn't matter where to practice.

447
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,580
What matters is what to practice.

448
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,280
Forget it, I won't say more.

449
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:19,920
Then,

450
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:22,440
do you need me to hire a dance teacher for you?

451
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,440
No need to bother.

452
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,480
I'll figure it out myself.

453
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:39,280
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

454
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:43,560
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

455
00:22:44,040 --> 00:22:46,440
Xinrui, good thing we chose your team.

456
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:48,240
Look at her dance moves.

457
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:50,120
It'll be hilarious if she performs that.

458
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:52,960
Exactly. What on earth are they practicing?

459
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:57,320
Four, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

460
00:22:58,640 --> 00:23:00,680
Yuanbao, let's stop practicing for now.

461
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,410
Let's take a two-minute break.

462
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:03,400
Yaqi.

463
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,800
Which country's dance are you practicing?

464
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:07,240
It's very unique.

465
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:11,090
Don't tell me it's your original creation, Yuanbao.

466
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,400
Yes, what's wrong?

467
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,400
Nothing.

468
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:15,640
Especially,

469
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,320
the dance is so awkward.

470
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:19,360
Exactly.

471
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:20,320
Dancing like you,

472
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:22,360
you might as well have quit last time,

473
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:24,360
so as not to waste time here.

474
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,280
Just practice yours.

475
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,560
Why do you care about us?

476
00:23:27,560 --> 00:23:28,360
Besides,

477
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:30,040
we haven't competed yet.

478
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:32,000
No one knows who will win or lose.

479
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:32,600
Yeah.

480
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:35,360
At least we dare to show it to everyone.

481
00:23:35,800 --> 00:23:36,720
What about you?

482
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:38,040
Being so sneaky,

483
00:23:38,040 --> 00:23:39,400
you might not even be as good as us.

484
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:40,000
Exactly.

485
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,920
We can't compare to you.

486
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,840
On this open-air playground,

487
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,160
you actually have the nerve to practice.

488
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,280
Our captain just

489
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:48,320
rented a dance studio

490
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,260
specifically for us to practice.

491
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:52,640
They even hired a professional dance teacher.

492
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:53,480
We really can't

493
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:54,840
compare with them.

494
00:23:55,320 --> 00:23:57,650
Yes, your captain is incredibly awesome.

495
00:23:57,680 --> 00:24:00,080
Then your captain should perform herself.

496
00:24:02,080 --> 00:24:04,200
I admit that I can't perform.

497
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:06,520
But you guys who did perform

498
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,600
didn't dance that well either.

499
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:10,200
Rather than bringing shame upon yourselves,

500
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,560
you'd be better off not performing.

501
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:12,400
What do you think?

502
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,360
Exactly.

503
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:15,440
Look at how terrible their dancing is.

504
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,560
They have no shame.

505
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:17,760
Are you done?

506
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:19,440
Then leave if you're done.

507
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,720
Don't interrupt our rehearsal.

508
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,480
Fine.

509
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:23,490
Let's not disturb their practice.

510
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,500
Who do they think they are?

511
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,040
But it seems they are actually

512
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:45,120
very well prepared.

513
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:47,560
They even hired a professional choreographer.

514
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:50,090
I also heard their costumes look really nice.

515
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:52,480
It's okay.

516
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,680
We practice less,

517
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:55,200
so it's normal that we are not good.

518
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,640
We'll be fine if we practice a few more times.

519
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,040
Come on, let's practice.

520
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,960
Yaqi, thank you.

521
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,000
Although you didn't participate,

522
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:04,120
you have been staying with us and encouraging us.

523
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:05,180
You are too polite.

524
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,170
Let's practice.

525
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:07,120
Yuanbao,

526
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:10,440
do you think what we are practicing

527
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,880
will really work?

528
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,400
Definitely.

529
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,540
Come on, let's continue practicing.

530
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:37,080
How long have you been practicing?

531
00:25:37,080 --> 00:25:38,440
Take a rest now.

532
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:40,840
No. My foundation is too weak.

533
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,680
If I don't work hard,

534
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,520
I'll drag everyone down.

535
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:50,200
Where are you hurt?

536
00:25:53,520 --> 00:25:54,600
Don't cry.

537
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,640
Does it hurt a lot?

538
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:58,120
Grandma.

539
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:01,200
Why am I so stupid?

540
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,040
Everyone trusts me so much

541
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:06,400
and chose me as the captain.

542
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:09,320
But what am I even dancing?

543
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:11,960
Even I think it looks ugly.

544
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,360
Silly girl.

545
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:16,240
Who dances perfectly

546
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,960
when they just start?

547
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:20,240
You have to believe in yourself.

548
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,640
You can definitely do it.

549
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,920
When you acted in that...

550
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,520
'A Chinese Odyssey' play,

551
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:28,200
didn't you go from zero to a hundred?

552
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,320
Acting is not dancing.

553
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:32,600
Although I memorized the moves,

554
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,400
my limbs are uncoordinated

555
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,800
and stiff.

556
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:38,520
I can't even keep up with the rhythm.

557
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,760
Moreover, these energetic dances

558
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:43,000
have fast moves and fast rhythms.

559
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:46,200
If I keep up with the first move, I miss the second.

560
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:49,920
If I catch the third, I miss the fourth.

561
00:26:50,520 --> 00:26:52,640
Everything is hard at the beginning.

562
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,600
If you can step on the first beat,

563
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:56,730
you can definitely step on the second.

564
00:26:56,760 --> 00:26:58,960
Let me tell you, when Grandma was young,

565
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:01,320
I also went from being uncoordinated

566
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:03,440
to dancing brilliantly.

567
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,560
Otherwise,

568
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:07,410
how could your grandpa pursue me so desperately?

569
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:11,520
You are my granddaughter.

570
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:13,000
You can definitely do it.

571
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:14,160
Don't cry.

572
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,920
I'll go get some medicine for you.

573
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:17,200
I'll teach you later.

574
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:20,770
Come, wait here.

575
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,760
What's wrong? Did I hurt your bones?

576
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:34,840
No, Grandma. You're pressing too hard.

577
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:37,520
Okay, I'll be gentler.

578
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,720
Come on, Yuanbao.

579
00:28:09,320 --> 00:28:10,600
You are the best.

580
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,480
When we were young,

581
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,160
we always thought there was

582
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:23,560
an unbridgeable gap between us and our parents.

583
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:24,620
Little did we know,

584
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:25,920
our every move

585
00:28:26,120 --> 00:28:28,360
is exactly how they were in their youth.

586
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:31,080
Because of us, parents

587
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,200
forget that they themselves

588
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,920
were once children too.

589
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:54,160
What are you trying to do this time?

590
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,020
Xiong Yuanbao.

591
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:57,360
I don't want to go against you.

592
00:28:57,360 --> 00:28:59,320
Haven't you gone against me enough?

593
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:00,980
I'll give you one more chance.

594
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,960
As long as you stay away from Meng Jingu,

595
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,040
I will quit the competition.

596
00:29:05,040 --> 00:29:06,160
And I promise

597
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:08,840
I won't make things difficult for you anymore.

598
00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:09,960
We will

599
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,160
leave each other alone.

600
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,620
Why should I listen to you?

601
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:17,720
You are bound to lose today's competition.

602
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,640
Why must you bring disgrace upon yourself?

603
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:21,970
What everyone has been saying these days,

604
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:24,400
you couldn't have missed it, right?

605
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,440
I heard it.

606
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:26,840
So what?

607
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,520
Since everyone chose me as the captain,

608
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:31,280
I must live up to their trust.

609
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:33,360
Until the very last moment of the competition,

610
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:35,020
I will absolutely not give up.

611
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,400
Live up to their trust?

612
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:38,820
Xiong Yuanbao,

613
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,160
is your so-called doing right by us

614
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:43,240
making everyone lose face with you?

615
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:46,040
If you leave, I'll quit.

616
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:48,000
That way, everyone saves face.

617
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:51,240
You can join the competition and be the captain,

618
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:53,300
and I won't have to look at you all day.

619
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:54,450
How nice.

620
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:57,560
I will fight for what I want.

621
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,220
I don't need your charity.

622
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:01,160
It's my freedom to do what I want.

623
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:03,330
You have no right to control me.

624
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:04,760
The competition hasn't started yet.

625
00:30:04,760 --> 00:30:06,320
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

626
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,410
You've got guts.

627
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,800
You'd better remember what you just said.

628
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:11,760
Today I will let you know

629
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:14,360
what a crushing defeat is.

630
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,040
Xiong Yuanbao.
